thread.title: Jared

author: Jared
title: Jared
text:
Cory from Quotacy was communicative, responsive, and informative. I did not know anything about life insurance when starting this process, but he helped me step by step identify my needs, and work with companies to get the best rate. There was never an upsell and the entire experience was focused around what was best for me.
It was so great I kept waiting for catch, but trust me, one never comes!
